'''女陰摩擦'''（{{lang|la|Tribadism、tribbing}}）、俗稱'''磨豆腐'''<ref>{{cite news|title=【美女與野獸．科普】違反自然？過千種動物有同性戀行為|url=https://www.hk01.com/01博評-百科/79459/美女與野獸-科普-違反自然-過千種動物有同性戀行為|publisher=香港01|author=吳俊熙|date=2017-03-22|accessdate=2018-08-29|archive-date=2018-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180927142909/https://www.hk01.com/01%E5%8D%9A%E8%A9%95-%E7%99%BE%E7%A7%91/79459/%E7%BE%8E%E5%A5%B3%E8%88%87%E9%87%8E%E7%8D%B8-%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE-%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E8%87%AA%E7%84%B6-%E9%81%8E%E5%8D%83%E7%A8%AE%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E6%9C%89%E5%90%8C%E6%80%A7%E6%88%80%E8%A1%8C%E7%82%BA|dead-url=no}}</ref>、'''磨鏡'''<ref>{{cite news|title=“磨镜”与“对食”：揭秘古代女同性恋(图)|url=http://cul.news.tom.com/2007-09-12/074A/09750582.html|publisher=TOM|date=2007-09-12|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090501191935/http://cul.news.tom.com/2007-09-12/074A/09750582.html|archivedate=2009-05-01|accessdate=2009-10-15}}</ref>，是性行為的一種，當中女性會以[[女陰|女陰]]磨擦其伴侶的身體部位以取得[[性刺激|性刺激]]，當中以摩擦[[陰蒂|陰蒂]]的情況最為普遍。此一行為的實踐方式包括女對女的[[性器官|性器官]]接觸、女性以其外陰摩擦其伴侣的大腿、腹部、臀部和手臂等口部以外的部位<ref name="Zimmerman">{{cite book|title =Lesbian histories and cultures: an encyclopedia (Volume 1)|publisher=Taylor & Francis|year=2000|pages=776–777| author =Bonnie Zimmerman|isbn = 0-8153-1920-7|url=https://books.google.com/?id=0EUoCrFolGcC&pg=PA777|accessdate=2012-02-29}}</ref><ref name="Belge">{{cite web|first=Kathy|last=Belge|title=What is Tribadism|accessdate=2010-12-19|publisher=[[About.com|About.com]]|url=http://lesbianlife.about.com/od/lesbiansex/f/Tribadism.htm|archive-date=2017-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170702213923/http://lesbianlife.about.com/od/lesbiansex/f/Tribadism.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author1=Cathy Winks  |author2=Anne Semans  |lastauthoramp=yes |title=The Good Vibrations Guide to Sex|publisher=Cleis Press|year=2002 | isbn=1-57344-158-9| edition=3rd}}</ref><ref name="Carroll">{{cite book|author=Janell L. Carroll|title=Sexuality Now: Embracing Diversity|isbn=0-495-60274-4|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2009|page=272|accessdate=2010-12-19|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5f8mQx7ULs4C&pg=PA272|archive-date=2013-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130615013659/http://books.google.com/books?id=5f8mQx7ULs4C&pg=PA272|dead-url=no}}</ref>。實踐者可以各種類型的性體位來實踐女陰摩擦，當中更包括[[傳教士體位|傳教士式體位]]<ref name="Hite, Tribadism">{{cite book | first = Shere| last = Hite | title = The Hite Report: A Nationwide Study of Female Sexuality | publisher = Seven Stories Press | year = 2004 | location=New York, NY | isbn = 1583225692| page=322 | accessdate =2012-03-02 | url =https://books.google.com/?id=s3OZaVn2wfkC&pg=PA322}}</ref><ref name="Schell">{{cite book|author =Jude Schell|title =Lesbian Sex: 101 Lovemaking Positions|isbn =0-495-60274-4|publisher=[[Random_House|Random House Digital]]|year=2008|page=18|accessdate= 2012-11-04|url=https://books.google.com/?id=JHVndzmgDmYC&pg=PP18}}</ref>。

「Tribadism」一詞常用於女女性行為的情景中，並於起初包含了以下社會信念的成分：女性擁有成為「插入之性」的性伴侶的能力<ref name="Zimmerman"/><ref name="Penner">{{Cite book| title=Mapping gender in ancient religious discourses | chapter=Still before sexuality: "Greek" androgyny, the Roman imperial politics of masculinity and the Roman invention of the ''Tribas''| publisher=Brill | year=2007 | isbn=90-04-15447-7|accessdate=February 19, 2012|url=https://books.google.com/?id=2udV9fAz1UkC&pg=PA11 |author1=Todd C. Penner |author2=Caroline Vander Stichele |pages=11–21}}</ref><ref name="Halberstam">{{cite book|first=Judith|last=Halberstam|title=Female Masculinity|isbn=9780822322436|publisher=Duke University Press|year=1998|pages=61–62|accessdate=2010-12-19|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=UYAi9OEYRekC&pg=PA61|archive-date=2013-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130613170916/http://books.google.com/books?id=UYAi9OEYRekC&pg=PA61|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在以往女性一旦被指責在性行為中成为插入的一方，便会遭到嘲笑或懲罰<ref name="Zimmerman"/><ref name="Halberstam"/><ref name="Goodman">{{cite book|title=Marie-Antoinette: writings on the body of a queen|author=Dena Goodman|publisher=Psychology Press|year=2003|pages=144–145|accessdate= 2012-02-19|isbn=0-415-93395-1|url=https://books.google.com/?id=VA9oTIyrWr4C&pg=PA145}}</ref>。在現代，此一用詞一般用於代指女性之間的各種[[非插入式性行為|非插入式性行為]]。在進行女陰摩擦的同時，人們可以[[指交|手指]]、[[假陰莖|假陰莖]]和[[雙頭假陰莖|雙頭假陰莖]]跟女性的陰道接合<ref name="Carroll"/><ref name="Halberstam"/>；此外它也可代指女性以其女陰摩擦长枕等非生命物體來達至[[性高潮|性高潮]]的自慰方式。
==歷史與文化==
===詞源及應用===
「tribadism」一詞源自於[[希臘語|希臘語]]τριβάς（tribas），其意是指「跟其他女性或獨自一人進行的不自然惡習」<ref>[http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.04.0057%3Aentry%3Dtriba%2Fs τριβάς] {{Wayback|url=http://www.perseus.tufts.edu/hopper/text?doc=Perseus%3Atext%3A1999.04.0057%3Aentry%3Dtriba%2Fs |date=20190603161147 }}, Henry George Liddell, Robert Scott, ''A Greek-English Lexicon'' on Perseus</ref>，對於古希臘人和古羅馬人而言，「tribas」或「tribade」<ref>''Oxford English Dictionary'' 2nd. Ed.</ref>皆在代指利用[[陰蒂|陰蒂]]或[[假陰莖|假陰莖]]跟他人（男性或女性）接合的雙性人或女性。在[[古典时代晚期|古典时代晚期]]以前，「tribade」一詞並不專門用於代指女性之間的性行為<ref name="Zimmerman"/><ref name="Halberstam"/> 。由於古希臘人和羅馬人還將任何涉及插入的性行為視作「男性所定義的性行為」，所以他們視「tribas」為最庸俗的女同性戀者<ref name="Penner"/><ref name="Halberstam"/><ref name="Norton">{{cite web |author=Rictor Norton |title=A Critique of Social Constructionism and Postmodern Queer Theory, "The 'Sodomite' and the 'Lesbian' |publisher=infopt.demon.co.uk |date=2002-07-12 |accessdate=2011-07-30 |url=http://www.infopt.demon.co.uk/social22.htm |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080215084530/http://www.infopt.demon.co.uk/social22.htm |archivedate=2008-02-15 }}</ref><ref name="Craven">{{cite book |author1=Sihvola, Juha |author2=Nussbaum, Martha Craven |title=The sleep of reason: erotic experience and sexual ethics in ancient Greece and Rome |url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_9780226609157 |publisher=University of Chicago Press |location=Chicago |year=2002 |isbn=0-226-60915-4}}</ref>。他們虽認可同性愛慕傾向的存在，但他們卻認為任何性行為皆需一名擁有陰莖的伴侶參與方可從事之，故此他們並不認為女性之間能存有任何的性行為，並對女女性行為者存有迷思——認為她們的陰蒂要不是腫脹肥大，就無法在性行為當中感到滿足<ref name="Blumenfeld">{{cite book|title =Looking at gay and lesbian life|publisher=Beacon Press|year=1993|page=93|isbn=0-8070-7923-5|accessdate= 2012-02-19|url=https://books.google.com/?id=WuJYskiyjEoC&pg=PA93|author=Warren J. Blumenfeld|author2=Diane Christine Raymond}}</ref><ref name="Skinner">"Invading the Roman Body: Manliness and Impenetrability in Roman Thought," pp. 30–31, and Pamela Gordon, "The Lover's Voice in ''Heroides'' 15: Or, Why Is Sappho a Man?," p. 283, both in ''Roman Sexualities''. {{cite book|title =Roman Sexualities|author=Marilyn B. Skinner|publisher=Princeton University Press|year=1997|page=14|isbn=0-691-01178-8|accessdate=2012-02-22|url=https://books.google.com/?id=1ZPC3TqBZEQC&pg=PA14}}</ref><ref name="Fredrick">"Look Who's Laughing at Sex: Men and Women Viewers in the ''Apodyterium'' of the Suburban Baths at Pompeii," in ''The Roman Gaze'', p. 168. The dildo is rarely mentioned in Roman sources, but was a popular comic item in Classical Greek literature and art; Richlin, "Sexuality in the Roman Empire," p. 351. {{cite book|title =The Roman Gaze: Vision, Power, and the Body|author=David Fredrick|publisher=JHU Press|year=2002|page=149|isbn=0-8018-6961-7|accessdate=2012-02-22|url=https://books.google.com/?id=KmVd4I2qvhwC&pg=PA149}}</ref><ref name="Clarke">Martial 1.90 and 7.67, 50; Richlin, "Sexuality in the Roman Empire," p. 347. {{cite book|title =Looking at lovemaking: constructions of sexuality in Roman art, 100 B.C.-A.D. 250, Part 250|author=John R. Clarke|publisher=University of California Press|year=2001|page=55|isbn=0-520-22904-5|accessdate=2012-02-22|url=https://books.google.com/?id=bwNdgd8cQcgC&pg=PA55}}</ref>。希臘和拉丁人早在1世紀後期便以此作諷刺的題材<ref name="Norton"/>。

「tribade」在英語的使用記錄最早可追溯至[[本·琼森|本·琼森]]的《前奏曲》（森林中的詩歌X，1601年）<ref name="Zimmerman"/>，最遲可至19世纪中；經由古典文學、解剖學、助產士、性愛指南和色情作品傳播後<ref name="Zimmerman"/>，這詞在過往便成為了歐洲最常見的女同性戀者用詞<ref name="Norton"/>。它於其後也用於代指女同性性行為，儘管18世纪中的解剖學調查最終引起了研究者對陰蒂肥大的定義懷疑，以及對更準確區分雌雄間性和陰蒂肥大的需求<ref name="Zimmerman"/>。

齊默爾曼這名著者指出：「歐洲人在很多時候會避免使用這個字詞，並以『不自然的惡習』、『猥褻行為』、『違反自然的罪行』、『使用一種手段』、『扮演男人的角色』等字句委婉地代指之」<ref name="Zimmerman"/>。在18世紀針對[[玛丽·安托瓦内特|安托瓦内特]]的[[诽谤|诽谤]]中，此一字詞變得常用起來。她在事件当中遭报刊「審判及嚴厲地定罪為」一名「tribade」<ref name="Zimmerman"/><ref name="Goodman"/>。古德曼認為「指責她為『tribade』的謠傳在歷史上具有特定的政治含義……《瑪麗 - 安托瓦內特懺悔錄》收錄了她的（虛構）最终声明：『人啊！因我屈服於大自然的甜蜜印象，並模仿法國宮廷內所有女性皆有的嫵媚弱點，所以我向愛的甜蜜衝動投降了……你抱着我，它就困在你的牆壁裡？』」。古德曼說明道，一項針對瑪麗 - 安托瓦內特的誹謗指其詳細描述了她丈夫「在性行為中失去行為能力」的細節，之後其欲望指向了[[勃利夫人|勃利夫人]]這名貴族，「接受了她的款待」。後來她又指與女性發生性關係的吸引力在於「机敏地刺激陰蒂的動作」。當時的诽谤指責安托瓦內特認為勃利夫人對她的愛慕產生「一種能夠取之不盡的罕見愉悅感，因為它能按一個人的需要不斷重復」<ref name="Goodman"/>。

在[[维多利亚时代|维多利亚时代]]，女陰摩擦被視為「低下階層及非西方文化所擁有的一種現象，並跟娼妓和罪犯的墮落有關」（引自齊默爾曼）<ref name="Zimmerman"/>。在20世紀，「tribade」一詞被「[[莎孚|sapphist]]」、「lesbian」（女同性戀）、 「invert」以及「homosexual」（兩者皆指同性戀）所取代，令「tribade」一詞顯得老舊起來<ref name="Zimmerman"/>。「Fricatrice」跟「tribade」屬同義，一樣能代指摩擦，但其詞根並非希臘語，而是拉丁語。前者早至1605年便在英語中使用（用在本·琼森的《前奏曲》中）<ref name="Andreadis">{{cite book |last=Andreadis |first=Harriette |title=Sappho in Early Modern England: Female Same-Sex Literary Erotics, 1550–1714|publisher=University of Chicago Press |year=2001 |pages=41, 49–51|isbn=0-226-02009-6}}</ref>「Fricatrice」比「tribade」更口語化及更具[[貶義|貶義]]<ref name="Andreadis"/>。此外還有拉丁語「confricatrice」和英語「rubster」等變體<ref name="Zimmerman"/><ref name="Andreadis"/>。
===實踐===
====性體位及盛行率====
女陰摩擦是一種常見於[[女女性行为者|女女性行為者]]當中的性行為<ref name="Carroll"/><ref name=" Zenilman & Shahmanesh">{{cite book | title = Sexually Transmitted Infections: Diagnosis, Management, and Treatment| publisher = Jones & Bartlett Publishers | year = 2011 | pages = 329–330 | accessdate =2012-11-04 |isbn = 0495812943| url = https://books.google.com/?id=lO5BND02eBwC&pg=PA329|quote= |author1=Jonathan Zenilman |author2=Mohsen Shahmanesh }}</ref><ref name="Greenberg">{{cite book|title=Exploring the Dimensions of Human Sexuality|isbn=9780763741488|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|year=2007|page=429|accessdate=2010-12-19|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZdYh_iFZvbkC&pg=PA429|author1=Jerrold S. Greenberg|author2=Clint E. Bruess|author3=Sarah C. Conklin|archive-date=2013-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015083408/http://books.google.com/books?id=ZdYh_iFZvbkC&pg=PA429|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kimmel">{{cite book|title=Lesbian, gay, bisexual, and transgender aging: research and clinical perspectives|isbn=9780231136181|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|year=2006|page=73|accessdate=2010-12-19|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Ae39o9m66hIC&pg=PA73|author1=Douglas C. Kimmel|author2=Tara Rose|author3=Steven David|archive-date=2015-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150315103333/http://books.google.com/books?id=Ae39o9m66hIC&pg=PA73|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管女陰摩擦一詞一般用於代指女陰對女陰的磨擦<ref name="Carroll"/><ref name="Westheimer">{{cite book | title = Encyclopedia of sex | publisher =Continuum | year = 2000 | page = 166 | accessdate = 2012-11-04 |isbn = 0826412408| url = https://books.google.com/?id=2EobAAAAYAAJ&q=&dq=|quote=A common variation is 'tribadism,' where two women lie face to face, one on top of the other. The genitals are pressed tightly together while the partners move in a grinding motion. Some rub their clitoris against their partner's pubic bone. | author = Ruth Karola Westheimer}}</ref>，但它也可代指其他性行為。除了令雙腳像兩把剪刀般互相交叉的交叉位外，適用於女陰摩擦的性體位還包括[[傳教士體位|傳教士式體位]]、[[女上位|女上位]]、[[後入體位|後入體位]]等<ref name="Hite, Tribadism"/><ref name="Schell"/>。從事女陰摩擦的女性亦能簡單地以其外陰摩擦其伴侶的大腿、腹部、臀部和手臂等部位<ref name="Belge"/><ref name="Schell"/><ref name="Crooks">{{cite book | title = Our Sexuality | publisher = Cengage Learning | year = 2010 | page = 239 | accessdate = 2012-11-04 |isbn = 0495812943| url = https://books.google.com/?id=MpRnPtmdRVwC&pg=PA239|quote=Rubbing genitals together or against other parts of a partner's body can be included in any couple's sexual interaction and is common in lesbian lovemaking... ...Many lesbians like [tribadism] because it involves all-over body contact and a generalized sensuality. Some women find the thrusting exciting; others straddle a partner's leg and rub gently. Some rub the clitoris on the partner's pubic pone (Loulan, 1984). |author1=Robert Crooks |author2=Karla Baur }}</ref>。在進行女陰摩擦的同時，[[指交|手指]]和[[假陰莖|假陰莖]]也可跟陰道接合。儘管有時「互利及回饋不是女陰摩擦的主要目標，但進行女陰摩擦的最明確目的在於『使雙方能夠透過不同方式感到滿意』」<ref name="Halberstam"/>。從事女陰摩擦或享受之的女性表示，她們能從中獲得愉悅感的地方包括身對身的全接觸、定期的臀部運動，以及其伴侶在身上移動的感覺；她們認為女陰摩擦擁有一定的刺激感、色欲感，以及因為女陰摩擦能使[[陰蒂|陰蒂]]得到充分刺激的缘故，所以其能使人更容易達至[[性高潮|高潮]]<ref name="Belge"/><ref name="Schell"/><ref name="Crooks"/>。
